text: Sup'Internet is a French private graduate school. It teaches things to do with the Internet. It was founded in 2011. Sup'Internet, la nouvelle école du web It is in Paris.IONIS Education Group annonce la création de Sup'Internet The school has three courses, graphic design, internet management and web technologies SUP'Internet accueille un Club des partenaires SUP’INTERNET, L'ÉCOLE SUPÉRIEURE DES MÉTIERS DU WEB and delivers a Bachelor's degree. Les métiers de l'Internet : le groupe Ionis lance Sup'Internet Deux nouvelles écoles dédiées à l'Internet It is one of the two schools in France (the other one is the École européenne des métiers de l'Internet) entirely meant for teaching things about the Internet.
